Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:34.45,Title screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,2250,6000,7700)\pos(274,384)\be1}Kibun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:34.45,Title screen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,2250,6000,7700)\pos(360,367)\fs20\be1}2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:34.45,MOT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,2250,4950,6200)}Presented by MOT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:45.98,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been half a year since we've started going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:53.02,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyday...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:01.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as I come to cook breakfast
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:04.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I become more accustomed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:09.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,his apartment’s kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This kind of thing makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.85,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's morning, Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.55,0:01:29.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, that hurts, the chopsticks are sticking into my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:31.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:34.75,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, my name is Nojima Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:38.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In case you didn't know I am the main character, hope we get along well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.15,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sticking in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.35,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! The chopsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:37.12,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopsticks!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:39.12,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:47.92,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be leaving first. You'd better hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:55.09,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, huh? That girl doesn't understand a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't ever change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, he's late again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:22.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Nami, he lives alone and spends all his time at his part time job right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're at it every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what are you saying, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:33.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, well, about once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.75,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young but it's only once a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.47,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:44.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I was able to I would, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He always just jumps on me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:50.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't even try to get me into the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His apartment is in this neighborhood right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go there in the morning so you can go to school together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That should be fine but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:07.13,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we're seen leaving together it will just look like we're coming out of a Love Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, it may be harsh on you but,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, Kenji Owada doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should definitely change horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:24.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really a person who suits me better than Kenji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.24,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Late again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Only if you didn't exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:42.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She may be a rarity who you'd want to protect but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.70,0:03:42.00,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:45.15,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:45.12,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what's so good about this slow poke of a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.15,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever the case, she's made her choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:51.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo~ Kenji-kun. Are you still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-Kun, don't you dare lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But of all people, why him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Level change!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:04.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:09.27,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you get a day off work, all you do is play games.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:13.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's hardly any time for the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I say we'd meet again tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but I was thinking about well, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:27.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that's what you meant? Why didn't you just say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.40,0:04:28.97,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-w-w-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:33.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not this suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always resist when I get to this part?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.38,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, just stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.07,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:45.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sounds like trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:56.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's so sudden I can't really tell if he likes me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:59.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:04.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I mean to Kenji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.90,0:05:15.65,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:19.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be redoing the test today after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what about our date?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! We'll have to do it some other time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad it wasn't during my part-time shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss would be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:38.25,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,469)}Due to unforeseen circumstances, please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the type who can protect herself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:51.05,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello everybody, I will now hand out the test papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.10,background Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~ Hey~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:57.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.02,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The angry one is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Owada, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.22,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! You wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:26.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Kiku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least look at the traffic lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway you're always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:46.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why" you say? You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, her panties are yellow today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.22,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambulance! Ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:00.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry Kenji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:07.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun got hurt because I was daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:10.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been inclined to daydream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.43,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were worried about me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.10,0:07:27.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to jump from the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.18,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:32.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stay like this a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nami. You're cutting it close again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:07.32,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I go visit Kenji-kun every morning to cook him breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:12.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun is running late again this morning, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:16.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's eating it after Nami made it then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.65,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do think Kenji-kun and I are made for each-other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:25.87,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and one day we'll be able to support each other’s weak points, I think it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.62,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.55,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a matter of waking up 10 minutes earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:36.16,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to ask {\i1}him{\i0} to wake up 10 minutes earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:40.55,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Nami gets even slower and starts waking me up later, I'm a goner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is already the start of summer vacation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:46.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this means I'll have a lot more time with Kenji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I told you to use the fan when you're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.44,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be better if the room was nice and cool when you returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, idiot, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:11.37,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the room is this cool, I don't really want to go to my part time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you take a day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.22,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're always so busy and we don't have any time to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun, do you not like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a boring reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:32.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's summer vacation, you're always at work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:37.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I come every day, I just wanted a bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you expecting from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For Kenji-kun to gently hold me from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.85,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and in those arms I lie lovingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:58.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,not understanding whether this time of happiness is a fleeting moment or eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:03.65,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then both of us turn to face each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:07.17,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,lips ready, we slowly close our eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:10.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're going to do it after that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:12.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:15.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're teasing me now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:15.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, you're not wearing a bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:30.35,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, well, it was hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make excuses, you really were teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not!
