Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:36.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This window is a perfect magic mirror, it just looks like a mirror from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.80,0:22:39.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look, you can see the pool down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.70,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, why do you think I chose this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:54.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see how you responded in a place where it feels like we're being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's running all the way down to your ankles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:01.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:11.33,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll slide in if you're this wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:15.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, it went in so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:21.45,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami you're off balance, stand up straighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:26.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, my legs are feeling so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:29.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Press up against the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:33.20,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:39.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun, my eyes met with someone below.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.30,0:23:41.10,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just imagining it, it's a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.53,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This magic mirror is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:48.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or not, if I remember correctly there is one place where you can see through.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:53.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, is it possible someone is watching us do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:23:57.60,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:05.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just, don't look, it's embarrassing, no, I'm going to cum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.50,0:24:33.80,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun hurry, you'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.80,0:24:38.90,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the rest of the holidays were spent doing homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.90,0:24:41.25,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be too obvious I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:42.95,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:45.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Door and windows closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.80,0:24:52.15,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The self I didn't even know was inevitably revealed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.40,0:24:55.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew I was so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.35,0:24:58.50,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:25:03.30,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's fine just the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.30,0:25:07.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many things which haven't chaged but everything feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.50,0:25:09.00,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
